{"tid":1786698,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國央行：香港基金走資約390億港元  約等於1.25% GDP","createTime":"2019-12-17T10:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T12:27:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"662d9826476eacff63235dbb4c51909cb88a25b0","tid":1786698,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.zd5xaEUZEdGPqSs_kAo_w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-12/14c52480-209d-11ea-bbf5-9a2459d38d79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.zd5xaEUZEdGPqSs_kAo_w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-12%2F14c52480-209d-11ea-bbf5-9a2459d38d79&h=937b2c47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港反修例示威衝突持續逾半年，無論是經濟，抑或民生都大受影響，市場一直擔心資金會否流出香港。據英倫銀行(英國央行)表示，由於香港的抗議示威活動愈演愈烈，已經有大約50億美元(約390億港元)資金由香港的投資基金中撤出。<br />\n<br />\n英倫銀行周一在其半年度金融穩定報告引述該行自己的計算以及Refinitiv、EPFR Global的數據指出，上述「走資」金額相當於香港GDP的1.25%左右。<br />\n<br />\n英倫銀行表示，目前英國銀行機構在香港的敞口總計約佔其普通股一級資本的大約160%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，香港兩家大型外資銀行滙豐控股及渣打集團已表示，自從4月開始的抗議示威活動以來，因投資者的擔憂情緒日益加劇，他們已注意到香港富戶在海外開設銀行帳戶。"},{"pid":"7ef2c37d617a2da0875c200c66f751d79290621c","tid":1786698,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69396c714446f41aed1374f516c2bc365153f8ed","tid":1786698,"uid":269481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3DArJGO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3DArJGO.gif&h=58b19689&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e931b4478d60665ff3d0e35c1b15ffd03b9c076d","tid":1786698,"uid":184903,"l